        <p class="mb-6">
          Engaging with GrowthWave Advisors or any of its divisions does not guarantee specific financial outcomes, investment returns, or financing approvals. All results depend on individual circumstances, market conditions, and applicable regulations.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #265077;">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mb-6">
          All content, branding, methodologies, and materials on this site are the property of GrowthWave Advisors LLC. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our written permission.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #265077;">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Questions about these terms? Reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@growthwaveadvisors.com" class="font-semibold underline" style="color: #51A7F8;">hello@growthwaveadvisors.com</a>.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 p-5 rounded-lg border" style="background: #f9fafb; border-color: #e5e7eb;">
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #718EA7;">
            <strong style="color: #595959;">Note:</strong> These terms are being expanded into a full legal agreement. For any questions in the meantime, please contact us directly.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer brand="advisors" />
</BaseLayout>
